{
	"Scope": "ScopeMathematics",

	"Sections": [
		{
			"Hash": "GlobalConfig",
			"Name": "Global Configuration",
			"Description": "Settings that affect calculations across all sections",
			"MetaTemplates":
				[
					{
						"HashPostfix": "-Template-Wrap-Prefix",
						"Template": "<h1>Scope Mathematics</h1><p>This example demonstrates cross-scope data access in solvers using <code>getGlobalFormData</code>, <code>resolveGlobalFormData</code>, <code>getSectionFormData</code>, and <code>getSectionTabularFormData</code>.</p><div><a href=\"#\" onclick=\"{~P~}.PictApplication.solve()\">[ solve ]</a> <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"{~P~}.views.PictFormMetacontroller.showSupportViewInlineEditor()\">[ debug ]</a></div><hr />"
					}
				],
			"Solvers":
				[
					{
						"Expression": "TotalItemsCost = resolveGlobalFormData(\"Summary.TotalItemsCost\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "TotalPartsCost = resolveGlobalFormData(\"Summary.TotalPartsCost\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "GrandTotal = TotalItemsCost + TotalPartsCost",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "DiscountedTotal = GrandTotal * (1 - (TaxRate / 100))",
						"Ordinal": 3
					}
				]
		},
		{
			"Hash": "Items",
			"Name": "Line Items",
			"Description": "A table of items with quantities and prices",
			"Groups": [
				{
					"Hash": "ItemList",
					"Name": "Item List",
					"Layout": "Tabular",
					"RecordSetAddress": "Items.ItemList",
					"RecordManifest": "ItemEditor",
					"RecordSetSolvers":
						[
							"LineTotal = Quantity * UnitPrice"
						]
				}
			],
			"Solvers":
				[
					{
						"Expression": "Summary.TotalItemsCost = SUM(ItemLineTotals)",
						"Ordinal": 2
					},
					{
						"Expression": "Summary.ItemCount = COUNT(ItemList)",
						"Ordinal": 2
					}
				]
		},
		{
			"Hash": "Parts",
			"Name": "Parts Inventory",
			"Description": "A second table to demonstrate cross-table data access",
			"Groups": [
				{
					"Hash": "PartList",
					"Name": "Parts",
					"Layout": "Tabular",
					"RecordSetAddress": "Parts.PartList",
					"RecordManifest": "PartEditor",
					"RecordSetSolvers":
						[
							"PartTotal = PartQuantity * PartCost"
						]
				}
			],
			"Solvers":
				[
					{
						"Expression": "Summary.TotalPartsCost = SUM(PartTotals)",
						"Ordinal": 2
					},
					{
						"Expression": "Summary.PartCount = COUNT(PartList)",
						"Ordinal": 2
					}
				]
		},
		{
			"Hash": "CrossScope",
			"Name": "Cross-Scope Calculations",
			"Description": "Demonstrates reading data from other sections using scope functions",
			"Solvers":
				[
					{
						"Expression": "CrossScopeItemTotal = getSectionFormData(\"Items\", \"Summary.TotalItemsCost\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "CrossScopePartTotal = getSectionFormData(\"Parts\", \"Summary.TotalPartsCost\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "CrossScopeGrandTotal = CrossScopeItemTotal + CrossScopePartTotal",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "GlobalTaxRate = getGlobalFormData(\"TaxRate\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "CrossScopeDiscounted = CrossScopeGrandTotal * (1 - (GlobalTaxRate / 100))",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "FirstItemName = getSectionTabularFormData(\"Items\", \"ItemList\", 0, \"ItemName\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "FirstItemTotal = getSectionTabularFormData(\"Items\", \"ItemList\", 0, \"LineTotal\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "FirstPartName = getSectionTabularFormData(\"Parts\", \"PartList\", 0, \"PartName\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					},
					{
						"Expression": "FirstPartTotal = getSectionTabularFormData(\"Parts\", \"PartList\", 0, \"PartTotal\")",
						"Ordinal": 3
					}
				]
		},
		{
			"Hash": "Summary",
			"Name": "Summary",
			"Description": "Aggregated totals computed from global scope"
		},
		{
			"Hash": "Documentation",
			"Name": "",
			"MetaTemplates":
				[
					{
						"HashPostfix": "-Template-Wrap-Prefix",
						"Template": "<hr /><h2>Solver Reference</h2><p>This example uses three solver ordinals to demonstrate execution order and cross-scope data access.</p><h3>Ordinal 1 &mdash; Row-Level RecordSetSolvers</h3><p>These run once per row in each tabular group, computing values within a single record.</p><table border='1' cellpadding='6' cellspacing='0' style='border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:1em;width:100%'><tr style='background:#ddd'><th>Section</th><th>Expression</th><th>Description</th></tr><tr><td>Items</td><td><code>LineTotal = Quantity * UnitPrice</code></td><td>Multiplies quantity by unit price for each line item row.</td></tr><tr><td>Parts</td><td><code>PartTotal = PartQuantity * PartCost</code></td><td>Multiplies quantity by cost for each part row.</td></tr></table><h3>Ordinal 2 &mdash; Section Aggregation Solvers</h3><p>These run after row solvers and aggregate tabular data into summary values. The <code>[].Property</code> descriptor syntax extracts a flat array of values from each row for use with <code>SUM</code>.</p><table border='1' cellpadding='6' cellspacing='0' style='border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:1em;width:100%'><tr style='background:#ddd'><th>Section</th><th>Expression</th><th>Description</th></tr><tr><td>Items</td><td><code>Summary.TotalItemsCost = SUM(ItemLineTotals)</code></td><td>Sums all LineTotal values via the <code>Items.ItemList[].LineTotal</code> collection extraction descriptor.</td></tr><tr><td>Items</td><td><code>Summary.ItemCount = COUNT(ItemList)</code></td><td>Counts the number of rows in the ItemList array.</td></tr><tr><td>Parts</td><td><code>Summary.TotalPartsCost = SUM(PartTotals)</code></td><td>Sums all PartTotal values via the <code>Parts.PartList[].PartTotal</code> collection extraction descriptor.</td></tr><tr><td>Parts</td><td><code>Summary.PartCount = COUNT(PartList)</code></td><td>Counts the number of rows in the PartList array.</td></tr></table><h3>Ordinal 3 &mdash; Cross-Scope Solvers</h3><p>These run last and demonstrate the four cross-scope data access functions.</p><h4><code>resolveGlobalFormData(address)</code></h4><p>Resolves a value from the global form data by manyfest address, using the metacontroller's <code>viewMarshalDestination</code> and <code>pict.manifest</code>.</p><table border='1' cellpadding='6' cellspacing='0' style='border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:1em;width:100%'><tr style='background:#ddd'><th>Section</th><th>Expression</th></tr><tr><td>GlobalConfig</td><td><code>TotalItemsCost = resolveGlobalFormData(\"Summary.TotalItemsCost\")</code></td></tr><tr><td>GlobalConfig</td><td><code>TotalPartsCost = resolveGlobalFormData(\"Summary.TotalPartsCost\")</code></td></tr></table><h4><code>getGlobalFormData(hash)</code></h4><p>Gets a value from the global form data by descriptor hash, using the global manyfest's <code>getValueByHash</code>.</p><table border='1' cellpadding='6' cellspacing='0' style='border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:1em;width:100%'><tr style='background:#ddd'><th>Section</th><th>Expression</th></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>GlobalTaxRate = getGlobalFormData(\"TaxRate\")</code></td></tr></table><h4><code>getSectionFormData(sectionHash, hashOrAddress)</code></h4><p>Gets a value from a specific section view's data using that section's <code>sectionManifest</code> and <code>getValueByHash</code>. Allows one section's solver to read another section's computed values.</p><table border='1' cellpadding='6' cellspacing='0' style='border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:1em;width:100%'><tr style='background:#ddd'><th>Section</th><th>Expression</th></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>CrossScopeItemTotal = getSectionFormData(\"Items\", \"Summary.TotalItemsCost\")</code></td></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>CrossScopePartTotal = getSectionFormData(\"Parts\", \"Summary.TotalPartsCost\")</code></td></tr></table><h4><code>getSectionTabularFormData(sectionHash, groupHash, rowIndex, hashOrAddress)</code></h4><p>Gets a value from a specific row of a tabular group in another section. Resolves the tabular record set, indexes into it by row, and uses the group's <code>supportingManifest</code> to look up the value by hash. The <code>rowIndex</code> parameter accepts both numbers and strings (for arbitrary precision compatibility).</p><table border='1' cellpadding='6' cellspacing='0' style='border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:1em;width:100%'><tr style='background:#ddd'><th>Section</th><th>Expression</th></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>FirstItemName = getSectionTabularFormData(\"Items\", \"ItemList\", 0, \"ItemName\")</code></td></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>FirstItemTotal = getSectionTabularFormData(\"Items\", \"ItemList\", 0, \"LineTotal\")</code></td></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>FirstPartName = getSectionTabularFormData(\"Parts\", \"PartList\", 0, \"PartName\")</code></td></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>FirstPartTotal = getSectionTabularFormData(\"Parts\", \"PartList\", 0, \"PartTotal\")</code></td></tr></table><h3>Computed Values (Ordinal 3)</h3><p>Standard arithmetic expressions that combine cross-scope results.</p><table border='1' cellpadding='6' cellspacing='0' style='border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:1em;width:100%'><tr style='background:#ddd'><th>Section</th><th>Expression</th><th>Description</th></tr><tr><td>GlobalConfig</td><td><code>GrandTotal = TotalItemsCost + TotalPartsCost</code></td><td>Sum of item and part totals pulled via resolveGlobalFormData.</td></tr><tr><td>GlobalConfig</td><td><code>DiscountedTotal = GrandTotal * (1 - (TaxRate / 100))</code></td><td>Applies the discount rate to the grand total.</td></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>CrossScopeGrandTotal = CrossScopeItemTotal + CrossScopePartTotal</code></td><td>Sum of totals pulled via getSectionFormData.</td></tr><tr><td>CrossScope</td><td><code>CrossScopeDiscounted = CrossScopeGrandTotal * (1 - (GlobalTaxRate / 100))</code></td><td>Applies tax rate pulled via getGlobalFormData.</td></tr></table>"
					}
				]
		}
	],

	"Descriptors":
